// - Calibrated GREEN / dual-band YELLOW / RED (same as your latest)
// - Heartbeat always on: 15s (known), 60s (UNKNOWN)
// - Posts "gray" to server when UNKNOWN (so backend sees off/sleep/unknown as gray)

